in%E2%80%93Brest_Offensive" title="Lublin–Brest Offensive">Lublin–Brest</a> – <a href="/wiki/Jassy%E2%80%93Kishinev_Offensive_(August_1944)" title="Jassy–Kishinev Offensive (August 1944)">Romania&#160;(Iassy–Kishinev)</a> – <a href="/wiki/Baltic_Offensive_(1944)" title="Baltic Offensive (1944)">Baltic</a> – <a href="/wiki/Budapest_Offensive" title="Budapest Offensive">Budapest</a> – <a href="/wiki/Vistula%E2%80%93Oder_Offensive" title="Vistula–Oder Offensive">Vistula–Oder</a> – <a href="/wiki/East_Prussian_Offensive" title="East Prussian Offensive">East&#160;Prussia</a> – <a href="/wiki/East_Pomeranian_Offensive" title="East Pomeranian Offensive">East&#160;Pomerania</a> – <a href="/wiki/Silesian_Offensives" title="Silesian Offensives">Silesia</a> – <a href="/wiki/Vienna_Offensive" title="Vienna Offensive">Vienna</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Berlin" title="Battle of Berlin">Berlin</a> – <a href="/wiki/Prague_Offensive" title="Prague Offensive">Prague</a></div>
